V0215_01_00_00_0.text: The human mind is too feeble to overcome my strategies!

V0215_01_00_01_0.text: Are you in a rush to meet your demise?

V0215_01_00_02_0.text: My Meklord Emperor will squash you like a pest!

V0215_01_00_03_0.text:
Meklord Emperor!
Send this fool spiraling into chaos!

V0215_01_00_04_0.text: I'm the one who will strike you down, Yusei Fudo!

V0215_01_00_05_0.text: When I defeat you, I'll snatch your Stardust Dragon!

V0215_01_00_06_0.text:
Don't order me around!
I do whatever I want!

V0215_03_00_00_0.text: It's only getting worse for you!

V0215_03_00_01_0.text: You're dancing in the palm of my hand!

V0215_03_00_03_0.text: How much more can you take before you fall to your knees?

V0215_03_00_04_0.text: Looks like this pest knows a few tricks.

V0215_03_00_05_0.text: No human is better than me!

V0215_05_00_00_0.text: My Meklord will crush everyone who stands in its path!

V0215_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my Set card!

V0215_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0215_16_00_01_0.text: You're as helpless as a bee who lost its stinger!

V0215_21_00_00_1.text: Now mount your attack, as fruitless as it will be!

V0215_21_00_01_0.text: I must admit - it's fun to watch you squirm!

V0215_21_00_03_1.text: If you want to survive, power your Circuit!

V0215_21_00_04_0.text: I still have enough Life Points left to defeat you!

V0215_21_00_05_0.text: How can this worm give me so much trouble!

V0215_28_00_00_0.text: You're nothing more than a worm crawling on the ground!

V0215_28_00_01_0.text: It was your destiny to kneel before my Meklord Emperor!

V0215_28_00_02_0.text: Synchros prove that humans can never truly evolve!

V0215_28_00_02_1.text: Because you spend all your time repeating the same mistakes!

V0215_28_00_03_0.text: I thought fate chose you because you were special.

V0215_28_00_04_0.text: Vanish along with this world, Yusei!

V0215_28_00_05_0.text: Synchro is far too great for a pest like you to wield!

V0215_28_00_05_1.text: You have failed, just like your Father!

V0215_28_00_06_0.text:
Hahahaha!
Look at that! You lost!

V0215_29_00_00_0.text: You're still nothing but a pest!

V0215_29_00_01_0.text: I will never accept that this pest defeated me!

V0215_29_00_02_0.text: How could a human defeat a Meklord Emperor?

V0215_29_00_03_0.text:
This isn't right!
This is impossible!

V0215_29_00_03_1.text:
This doesn't make sense!
The whole world doesn't make sense!

V0215_29_00_04_0.text: Yusei Fudo, I will get my revenge!

V0215_33_00_01_0.text: The power of the Meklords is infinite!

V0215_33_00_02_0.text:
I'll show you my true power!
Haaaaaa!

V0215_30_00_00_0.text: Have you ever seen a bee dance?

V0215_30_00_01_0.text: You may think you're in control, but you can't change fate.

V0215_30_00_02_0.text: Wander aimlessly until you can wander no more!

V0215_34_00_00_0.text: Let me see you dance like a bee!

V0215_34_00_01_0.text: That's the best you can do?

V0215_34_00_02_0.text: Are you trying to put me to sleep?

V0215_34_00_03_0.text: Trying to win with the same old moves?

V0215_34_00_04_0.text: Hahaha! You used Synchro Summons against a Meklord Emperor?

V0215_34_00_05_0.text: Whoever wields that card can easily become the King!

V0215_34_00_06_0.text: It's your fault for not paying attention.

V0215_34_00_09_0.text: There's nothing more sad than having no one to love.

V0215_35_00_00_0.text: My Meklord will prove how weak you are!

V0215_36_00_04_0.text:
I did everything I could!
So live with it!

V0215_08_00_00_0.text: I activate my Field Spell, Meklord Fortress!

V0215_08_00_00_1.text: Synchro Monsters can no longer affect Meklord Emperors!

V0215_08_00_01_0.text: When Meklord Fortress is destroyed, its effect activates!

V0215_08_00_01_1.text: I add one Meklord Emperor in my deck to my hand!

V0215_08_00_02_0.text: I activate the Continuous Spell, Meklord Assembly!

V0215_08_00_03_1.text: I discard a card to destroy one monster on my field!

V0215_08_00_04_0.text: When a Meklord is destroyed, Meklord Assembly activates!

V0215_08_00_04_1.text: It destroys one face-up Spell or Trap Card!

V0215_08_00_05_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Reboot!

V0215_08_00_05_1.text: I return a Meklord to my deck to get another Meklord card!

V0215_08_00_06_0.text: I activate the Quick-Play Spell, Limiter Removal!

V0215_08_00_07_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Mektimed Blast!

V0215_08_00_07_1.text: It destroys my Meklord and one card on your field!

V0215_08_00_08_0.text: I activate the Continuous Trap, DNA Surgery!

V0215_08_00_08_1.text: All face-up monsters change to the Type of my choosing!

V0215_08_00_09_0.text: I activate the Continuous Trap, DNA Transplant!

V0215_08_00_09_1.text: All face-up monsters change to the Attribute of my choice!

V0215_08_00_10_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Trap Stun!

V0215_08_00_10_1.text: All other Trap Cards are negated this turn!

V0215_08_00_11_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Torrential Tribute!

V0215_08_00_11_1.text: All monsters on the field are destroyed!

V0215_08_00_12_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Twin Vortex!

V0215_08_00_13_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Spark Breaker!

V0215_08_00_15_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Labyrinth of Kline!

V0215_08_00_16_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Battle Return!

V0215_08_00_17_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Divergence!

V0215_08_00_19_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Convert Ghost!

V0215_08_00_20_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Infinity Force!

V0215_08_00_21_0.text: I activate my Continuous Trap, Infinite Prison!

V0215_09_00_00_0.text: An effect destroyed my monster, so I Special Summon this!

V0215_09_00_01_0.text: I use Meklord Emperor Wisel's effect to Special Summon it!

V0215_09_00_02_0.text: Meklord Emperor Wisel absorbs your Synchro Monster!

V0215_09_00_03_0.text: Your Synchro Monster will fuel my Meklord's strength!

V0215_09_00_04_0.text: Meklord Emperor Wisel negates and destroys your Spell!

V0215_09_00_05_0.text: I use Meklord Emperor Skiel's effect to Special Summon it!

V0215_09_00_06_0.text: Meklord Emperor Skiel! Absorb that Synchro Monster!

V0215_09_00_07_0.text: I send a monster equipped to my Skiel to the Graveyard!

V0215_09_00_07_1.text: It can now attack you directly this turn!

V0215_09_00_08_0.text: I use Meklord Emperor Granel's effect to Special Summon it!

V0215_09_00_09_0.text: Meklord Emperor Granel snatches your Synchro Monster!

V0215_09_00_10_1.text: It Special Summons a monster that's equipped to it!

V0215_09_00_11_0.text: I send a Meklord to the Graveyard to Special Summon this!

V0215_09_00_12_0.text: By Special Summoning it, one of your monsters can't attack!

V0215_09_00_13_0.text: I Tribute this card to negate and destroy that card!

V0215_09_00_14_0.text: When Ally Salvo is destroyed, I can destroy two cards!

V0215_13_00_00_0.text:
Combine into one!
Meklord Emperor Wisel!

V0215_13_00_01_0.text: Do you feel a dark shadow of doom closing around you?

V0215_13_00_01_1.text: It’s the shadow cast by my Meklord Emperor Wisel!

V0215_13_00_03_0.text: Jakob's card, give me your power!

V0215_13_00_04_0.text:
Power up!
Meklord Emperor Wisel - Synchro Absorption!

V0215_19_00_01_0.text:
Meklord Emperor Skiel!
Let 'em have it!

V0215_19_00_03_0.text:
Meklord Emperor Wisel - Synchro Absorption!
Take 'em down!
